description: Incorrect course internal id when requireing internal id.
Correct course idnumber when requiring internal id.
Course id, type, module, instance, number and item name are sufficient for adding an item.
Item type and item module are ignored.
Item idnumber can be a number.
Item idnumber can contain non-alphanumeric characters.
Item max grade can be less than 100.
Item max grade can be greater than 100.
Item can be added to grade category.
Updated item does not require item name.
Updated item can move to another category.
